thread.title: Stephanie Hively
thread.title_full: California Casualty Auto and Home Insurance reviewed by Stephanie Hively

author: Stephanie Hively
title: Stephanie Hively
text: My ceiling fell in due to faulty pipes. I live in a condo. California Casualty sent an agent out quicker than the insurance company that provided the condo's master policy. I never had to stay after Californis Casualty about my coverage. I ended up calling the national office to get the master policy to handle my claim properly
